{"tid":1104291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]我隻貓㢌血","createTime":"2019-04-13T04:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T17:32:23.000Z","uid":70146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c6b6a6fce1577e263365405f256acb0533473b","tid":1104291,"uid":70146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"話說係清明嘅時間我發覺佢去多咗廁所 咁我就帶佢去睇醫生就話膀胱有晶石磨到所以發炎 咁開咗D藥我一直都有餵佢食藥 今個星期日本身複診啦<br />\n點知 到咗佢突然間入咗我間房（入邊都有一個貓砂盆）不停咁樣坐係入邊 每隔30秒就去坐一坐 但係all出嚟得好少 有時直頭冇 <br />\n到咗三四點時間仲滴血 今朝餵藥嘅時候嘔返晒出嚟 之後我諗住今日12:00放工即刻帶佢去睇醫生 或者將個booking提早 點知我今朝佢一開門嘅時候打過去 佢話full左Booking 跟住叫我打去其他地方我打每一間都話full左  請問大家有冇一啲真係真心好嘅醫生推介？？ 心急人上<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oW85tOv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoW85tOv.png&h=593d60b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50a71ae4004e17961dfe114414e2172920d749f6","tid":1104291,"uid":70146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccd8b600fc959ea7b36ce1368bd55750898f11a","tid":1104291,"uid":70146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T05:00:29.000Z","msg":"救救我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmo